# Frameworks Rules

Framework/tool-specific rules that apply when using these frameworks or tools.

## Database

- `connection-management.mdc` - Database connection principles (ORM-agnostic)
- `prisma.mdc` - Prisma database patterns for Next.js/TypeScript
- `supabase.mdc` - Supabase development guidelines and patterns
- `sqlalchemy.mdc` - SQLAlchemy patterns for Python
- `alembic.mdc` - Alembic migration patterns for Python

## UI

- `tailwind-css.mdc` - Tailwind CSS styling standards
- `tamagui.mdc` - Tamagui property mappings and component development

## Testing

- `standards.mdc` - Testing standards - no mocking of internal systems
- `organization.mdc` - Test organization, file layout, coverage targets
- `tools.mdc` - Testing tools and commands

## Usage

These rules apply automatically when files matching the glob patterns are present. See individual rule files for specific glob patterns.

